{"tid":2262072,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔你好 關於block人我有少少建議","createTime":"2020-10-28T21:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T09:27:19.000Z","uid":132326,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ba66459c1f6074335a420ba0df9f9b7fbeab3bb7","tid":2262072,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T21:22:33.000Z","msg":"就係可以整個封鎖原因嘅template<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時block人原因可以由對方嘅一個post或者留言就諗返起，所以其實個原因好多時附上個post link加樓層就夠了<br />\n<br />\n個template可以係類似<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/12345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/12345</a> #10<br />\n<br />\n或者我唔知連登係咪每個層數都有anchor 如果有用anchor仲方便<br />\n<br />\n咁樣比冇description informative好多 而且想追擊五毛嗰陣可以用嚟做證據/reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果喺block list度可以按到原因上嘅link成件事就梗係更加完滿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decf4c644def3f41611d0b4befb739bcbd527f04","tid":2262072,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a3fba661b74c4e2d03ad620b8e210b77d4ac03","tid":2262072,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"連仔快覆"},{"pid":"4f7a909a59748dfec50c3b913b98f278c73053be","tid":2262072,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"連"}]}